{
  "stem": "26142.11",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I as-- and when I woke up, I see him sitting at the table talking to my older brother, Tsvi, and asking, ask-- asking questions about what happened.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where is Moshe, you know, the rest of the family?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] I jumped out of bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CRYING] I noticed right away that my father aged in those four months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CRYING] Anyway, it was a happy, happy reunion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And not too far from Chust-- I told-- I told the story before, that we sent some stuff away to my father's sister that lived close by-- only twenty kilometers from the city of Chust.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in among those things, I had-- my clothing were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said he is going to go travel back to Berezovo-- was the name of the place he traveled back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came with his sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came the next day again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was-- this took another day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were already at, at that time in this David Schwartz's house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he brought us some fresh clothing for, for both of us, for Tsvi and for myself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also we asked him to bring-- to bring a, a, a shaver-- a shaver and a-- and a-- and a hair cutter because we were filthy, filthy with lice after so many months.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And of course, when he came the next day with his sister, they brought-- they brought fresh clothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and the-- his sister started asking about the rest of the family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we, we just told them simply that we don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, we knew that so-- that what was going on at Kamenets-Podol'skii, that they, they, they, they, they are not alive anymore.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
